<br>
Have you every fought shadow men zoner?  Talk about fast.  They can even catch my lvl 49 bard with selo's on!  They will catch you sowed or with Jboots in like your standing still as well as quite a few of them pop as casters.   Ever tried to quad kit with a caster?  I did once...and will never even attempt it again..thank god I had a partner with me that was able to solo the caster..while I did the other 3.<br>
