Quadding Shadowmen = Recipe for Disaster!<br>
Nunarie Erianun <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaniar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aniar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 7:19:09 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RE: Old World Quadding sites?</span><hr size=1> Not quadding, but I've been able to dual the Aviak avocets and harriers in SK pretty successfully at 29.  Just lev yourself, run partway up the ramp.  If the ramp is camped at the bottom, you can get about halfway up, and you can see an avocet in a hut, and be able to see a harrier outside a hut further up the ramp.  target the harrier, SoTF him and run.  You'll be close enough to the avocet that you'll aggro him as well.  Since you've got Lev on, you can just jump off the ramp.  Run them into the open, turn circles to get 'em close enough together, BoF, and nuke to hell.  Normally the avocet will last longer than the harrier (he's yellow to me, the harrier's blue), but that means you can use inferno shock on him to finish him off.<br>
WORD OF WARNING:  I've ran out of mana a few times doing this, BUT if I keep Lightning shock (from lvl 12) in my 3rd slot (2dd, lightning shock, 2AoE pillars, skin, bof, yonder, gate) I can chase him down to melee to death, and and have a low-mana spell that comes up fairly quickly.  Every time I've ran out of mana the avocet's been running, so it's been a safe thing to melee. <p><br>Aniar Orrenson
<br>Wizard of the 29th Season
<br>High Councilman of the Nightwatch of Norrath
<br>"You look up overkill in the dictionary and there's a picture of Aniar lol" Lotta on Saryrn</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showMessage?topicID=133.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showMessage?topicID=136.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.emailToFriend?topicID=87.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.threadControl?topicID=87.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=87.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=87.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Man